1. Install Docker

2. Run `autoconf`

3a. For server run:
./configure MODE=server DB_PASSWORD="!@#%" DOMAIN_NAME="206.12.59.179" WORKERS_SUBNET="192.168.125.0/24" CLIENT_MAX_BODY_SIZE=200M RODAN_DATA_DIR=/mnt/rodan_data

3b. For worker, run:
./configure MODE=worker DB_PASSWORD="!@#%" DB_HOST="192.168.125.2" CELERY_BROKER_URL="amqp://rodanuser:DDMALrodan@192.168.125.2:5672/DDMAL" SERVER_IP="192.168.125.2"

4. Copy Kakadu source code in this folder (e.g. v7_7-01273N.zip)

5. Run `sh deploy.sh`


